{"about_the_game":"<i>COLD DEPTH is a first person survival horror game about exploring underwater stations in the near future.</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/Fauna.gif?t=1724658311\" /><br><br><strong>EVERYTHING WENT WRONG</strong><br>The year is 2030. In the Black Sea, due to a record increase in water salinity and strange oxygen emissions, a lot of minerals have been found.<br>It is here, in the Black Sea at a depth of two thousand meters, that there is an underwater complex - &quot;Oasis&quot;,<br>It was recently built by the independent corporation &quot;AO&quot; (&quot;Atlantic Union&quot;), which is engaged in the extraction, purification and supply of minerals from the seabed.<br><br>The main character Lisa goes to work at a drilling station, but everything went wrong. Whether she will survive or die depends only on you. Save her.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366650/extras/EA_ReplaceReactorCore.gif?t=1724658311\" /><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stations power management.<br></li><li>Physics-based interactions. 90% Objects in the game are physics interactive.<br></li><li>Recycling, 3D Printing and Packing objects in movable inventory.<br></li><li>Character parameters and effects.<br></li><li>Replacing broken parts with new ones (printed on our 3d printers).</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Enjoy your stay","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1366650/208304423737d193e7523a22899acb2b0573ba9d.jpg"},{"name":"Triple-double","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1366650/3c7d230b3aafcd7fd0a6bf3cf010c6179289c4a9.jpg"},{"name":"Overhaul","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1366650/f78dd3b22556805404209ad16f16fce8603a6212.jpg"},{"name":"Look